## Commands
- `pnpm dev` - Start both frontend and backend
- `pnpm dev:client` - Start frontend only
- `pnpm dev:server` - Start backend only
- `pnpm build` - Build both for production
- `pnpm test` - Run all tests

## Development Notes
- Shared types go in shared/ directory
- API proxy configured in client Vite config
- Use pnpm workspaces for dependencies
